00:30:27,619 --> 00:30:29,259
[SPEAKER_02] pacificiranje,

825
00:30:29,259 --> 00:30:30,059
[SPEAKER_02] mislim da tu nema

826
00:30:30,059 --> 00:30:31,359
[SPEAKER_02] nijednog pacificiranja,

827
00:30:31,359 --> 00:30:31,779
[SPEAKER_02] ali da.

828
00:30:31,779 --> 00:30:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] u dalekoj budućnosti,

829
00:30:34,079 --> 00:30:35,799
[SPEAKER_00] u dalekoj budućnosti.

830
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] Pa mislim da je neka,

831
00:30:38,559 --> 00:30:42,880
[SPEAKER_02] neka arapska ideja,

832
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:43,700
[SPEAKER_02] ajde recimo,

833
00:30:43,700 --> 00:30:45,380
[SPEAKER_02] možda arabijska ideja,

834
00:30:45,380 --> 00:30:46,519
[SPEAKER_02] ajde da tako kažemo,

835
00:30:46,519 --> 00:30:47,019
[SPEAKER_02] ali su,

836
00:30:47,019 --> 00:30:50,140
[SPEAKER_02] ali su možda više nekako gledali na to da,

837
00:30:50,140 --> 00:30:52,319
[SPEAKER_02] da se pričeka,

838
00:30:52,319 --> 00:30:56,920
[SPEAKER_02] da prirodno odu lideri Islamske republike,

839
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:58,599
[SPEAKER_02] su svi preko 80 govina

840
00:30:58,599 --> 00:31:02,160
[SPEAKER_02] i to zapravo na neki način,

841
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:02,599
[SPEAKER_02] evo,

842
00:31:02,599 --> 00:31:06,339
[SPEAKER_02] moj utisak je da i narod to čeka u Iranu,

843
00:31:06,339 --> 00:31:09,779
[SPEAKER_02] kako bi onda došlo nešto novo,

844
00:31:09,779 --> 00:31:10,319
[SPEAKER_02] nešto

845
00:31:10,319 --> 00:31:14,420
[SPEAKER_02] fleksibilnije, da tako kažemo,

846
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:15,420
[SPEAKER_02] je li nešto što

847
00:31:15,420 --> 00:31:17,220
[SPEAKER_02] što odgovara

848
00:31:17,220 --> 00:31:19,299
[SPEAKER_02] nekim drugim interesima.

849
00:31:19,299 --> 00:31:20,400
[SPEAKER_02] Evo,

850
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,980
[SPEAKER_02] daću vam jedan,

851
00:31:21,980 --> 00:31:23,200
[SPEAKER_02] jednu možda,

852
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:26,819
[SPEAKER_02] možda nije toliko točna

853
00:31:26,819 --> 00:31:29,900
[SPEAKER_02] usporedba,

854
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:33,019
[SPEAKER_02] ali otprilike je to tu negdje.

855
00:31:33,019 --> 00:31:36,519
[SPEAKER_02] Iran danas je Jugoslavije 80.

856
00:31:36,519 --> 00:31:41,140
[SPEAKER_02] Postoji sustav koji nekako funkcionira.

857
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:43,740
[SPEAKER_02] Nitko ne vjerujete sustav,

858
00:31:43,740 --> 00:31:45,619
[SPEAKER_02] osim onih baš ona okorijalih,

859
00:31:45,619 --> 00:31:47,099
[SPEAKER_02] starih i nekih ljudi

860
00:31:47,099 --> 00:31:49,099
[SPEAKER_02] koji podržavaju taj sustav.

861
00:31:49,099 --> 00:31:50,980
[SPEAKER_02] Ali zapravo drugi su pragmatici,

862
00:31:50,980 --> 00:31:54,079
[SPEAKER_02] drugi samo izvlače iz tog sustava

863
00:31:54,079 --> 00:31:54,980
[SPEAKER_02] sve što mogu

864
00:31:54,980 --> 00:31:58,000
[SPEAKER_02] kako bi osigurali sebi neku budućnost.

865
00:31:58,000 --> 00:32:01,359
[SPEAKER_02] I to je sustav koji zapravo

866
00:32:01,359 --> 00:32:03,819
[SPEAKER_02] u konačici ne može preživjeti.

867
00:32:03,819 --> 00:32:05,279
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, on se mora mijenjati,

868
00:32:05,279 --> 00:32:06,680
[SPEAKER_02] on se mora transformirati.

869
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] Može biti Islamska republika,

870
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:09,559
[SPEAKER_02] to i dalje,

871
00:32:09,980 --> 00:32:12,119
[SPEAKER_02] ali ona neće biti ista kao što je sada

872
00:32:12,119 --> 00:32:13,319
[SPEAKER_02] kada ih vodite ovi,

873
00:32:13,319 --> 00:32:14,440
[SPEAKER_02] da tako kažem,

874
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:14,980
[SPEAKER_02] tuzolimi.

875
00:32:14,980 --> 00:32:16,240
[SPEAKER_02] Jednostavno,

876
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,779
[SPEAKER_02] oni su zarobljeni

877
00:32:17,779 --> 00:32:20,400
[SPEAKER_02] u svojim 70-ima i 80-ima

878
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:22,240
[SPEAKER_02] kada su vodili revoluciju

879
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:23,440
[SPEAKER_02] i rat protiv Iraka.

880
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,259
[SPEAKER_02] I oni ne mogu pobjeći iz toga.

881
00:32:25,259 --> 00:32:27,319
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan ajatolah jednom

882
00:32:27,319 --> 00:32:28,720
[SPEAKER_02] jako lijepo to opisao,

883
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:29,059
[SPEAKER_02] mislim,

884
00:32:29,059 --> 00:32:30,500
[SPEAKER_02] zgodno je opisao,

885
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:32,119
[SPEAKER_02] da je njihova revolucija

886
00:32:32,119 --> 00:32:33,019
[SPEAKER_02] kao bicikla,

887
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,500
[SPEAKER_02] ako stane, pada.

888
00:32:34,500 --> 00:32:36,759
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, oni moraju stalno,

889
00:32:36,759 --> 00:32:38,700
[SPEAKER_02] kao i u jugi kad je to bilo,

890
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:40,299
[SPEAKER_02] znate, stalno se ponavljala

891
00:32:40,299 --> 00:32:41,660
[SPEAKER_02] narodno-slobalačka borba,

892
00:32:41,660 --> 00:32:42,380
[SPEAKER_02] pratstvo, jedinstvo,

893
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,400
[SPEAKER_02] sve te parole,

894
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:46,059
[SPEAKER_02] sve te stvari moraju postojati

895
00:32:46,059 --> 00:32:48,480
[SPEAKER_02] kako bi se legitimitet sustava

896
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] mogao nastaviti

897
00:32:49,559 --> 00:32:50,920
[SPEAKER_02] i kako bi cijeli sustav,

898
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,420
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno ljudi unutar sustav

899
00:32:52,420 --> 00:32:54,059
[SPEAKER_02] mogli od tog sustava živjeti.

900
00:32:54,059 --> 00:32:56,980
[SPEAKER_02] To je velika nepotizam

901
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:57,980
[SPEAKER_02] je naravno nastavno

902
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:58,880
[SPEAKER_02] temelju toga,

903
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:02,339
[SPEAKER_02] ali fleksibilnost je ipak nešto

904
00:33:02,339 --> 00:33:03,640
[SPEAKER_02] što oni traže,

905
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:05,859
[SPEAKER_02] ali ne mogu dobiti sve

906
00:33:05,859 --> 00:33:07,900
[SPEAKER_02] dok postoje te revolucionarne ideje

907
00:33:07,900 --> 00:33:08,819
[SPEAKER_02] koje su žive.

908
00:33:08,819 --> 00:33:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Štijela sam vas pitati,

909
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] bili ste u Iranu,

910
00:33:12,380 --> 00:33:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] kako se zapravo tamo živi?

911
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:19,240
[SPEAKER_00] Kako obični ljudi žive?

912
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:22,579
[SPEAKER_02] Iran je u kontekstu

913
00:33:22,579 --> 00:33:23,920
[SPEAKER_02] nekog bliskog istoka

914
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:25,359
[SPEAKER_02] to sve normalna zemlja.

915
00:33:25,359 --> 00:33:27,619
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, nije to ništa,

916
00:33:27,619 --> 00:33:31,440
[SPEAKER_02] život je težak

917
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:33,420
[SPEAKER_02] kao da nije negde drugdje,

918
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:35,099
[SPEAKER_02] ne znam, u Iraku ili

919
00:33:35,099 --> 00:33:37,019
[SPEAKER_02] bore je u arapskim zemljama

920
00:33:37,019 --> 00:33:38,440
[SPEAKER_02] po mojem osobnom mišljenju,

921
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:41,059
[SPEAKER_02] ali u Iranu

922
00:33:41,059 --> 00:33:45,019
[SPEAKER_02] Iran funkcionira po pitanju

923
00:33:45,019 --> 00:33:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] velikog socijalnog populizma.

924
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:48,859
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, sve je besplatno.

925
00:33:48,859 --> 00:33:51,059
[SPEAKER_02] Sve je od školovanja,

926
00:33:51,059 --> 00:33:51,960
[SPEAKER_02] medicine,

927
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:53,700
[SPEAKER_02] ne znam,

928
00:33:53,700 --> 00:33:55,920
[SPEAKER_02] kulturnih uzdisni,

929
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:57,380
[SPEAKER_02] to je užasno kulturno zemlje.

930
00:33:57,500 --> 00:33:59,480
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, to je zemlja koja ima

931
00:33:59,480 --> 00:34:00,799
[SPEAKER_02] vrlo vjerojatno

932
00:34:00,799 --> 00:34:02,960
[SPEAKER_02] jedan od najvećih stopa

933
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,960
[SPEAKER_02] konzumiranja svakodnevne kulture.

934
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:06,839
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, ja ne znam

935
00:34:06,839 --> 00:34:09,320
[SPEAKER_02] drugu zemlju gdje su krcati kazališta,

936
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,679
[SPEAKER_02] krcate kinak,

937
00:34:10,679 --> 00:34:13,420
[SPEAKER_02] krcate poetske večeri,

938
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:14,280
[SPEAKER_02] jel i tako dalje.

939
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,019
[SPEAKER_02] Sa druge strane,

940
00:34:16,019 --> 00:34:18,239
[SPEAKER_02] imaju vrlo snažnu

941
00:34:18,239 --> 00:34:19,960
[SPEAKER_02] znanstvenu zajednicu.

942
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:22,340
[SPEAKER_02] Trenutačno proizvodnje znanja

943
00:34:22,340 --> 00:34:24,480
[SPEAKER_02] kolektivnosti u 17. na svijetu

944
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:26,960
[SPEAKER_02] i 13. u biomedicinskim znanostima.

945
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:30,739
[SPEAKER_02] Imaju iznimno razvijenu industriju,

946
00:34:30,739 --> 00:34:33,619
[SPEAKER_02] iznimno razvijenu obrtništvo,

947
00:34:33,619 --> 00:34:36,019
[SPEAKER_02] ali sve je unutar zemlje.

948
00:34:36,019 --> 00:34:38,639
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, to je unutarnja ekonomija

949
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:40,340
[SPEAKER_02] koja funkcionira samo tamo.

950
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:41,980
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam bio u drugom mjesecu

951
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:43,380
[SPEAKER_02] i sad mi čovjek kaže,

952
00:34:43,380 --> 00:34:45,480
[SPEAKER_02] evo, ba tu se otvorilo 30 novih

953
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:47,820
[SPEAKER_02] tvornica, sad rade kao neke

954
00:34:47,820 --> 00:34:49,699
[SPEAKER_02] parkete, ne znam,

955
00:34:49,699 --> 00:34:50,840
[SPEAKER_02] pločice i te stvari.

956
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:52,079
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim, 30, pazite,

957
00:34:52,079 --> 00:34:53,460
[SPEAKER_02] gdje u Hrvatskoj vi imate

958
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:54,980
[SPEAKER_02] da se otvori 30 novih.

959
00:34:54,980 --> 00:34:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ma gdje imate jednu?

960
00:34:56,300 --> 00:34:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

961
00:34:57,679 --> 00:34:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] A hvala li te.

962
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:05,519
[SPEAKER_02] Sustav brine da nitko nije gladan,

963
00:35:05,519 --> 00:35:07,219
[SPEAKER_02] iako postoje, naravno,

964
00:35:07,219 --> 00:35:08,159
[SPEAKER_02] siromošni ljudi,

965
00:35:08,159 --> 00:35:10,340
[SPEAKER_02] ali nećete naći nikoga da kopa po smeću

966
00:35:10,340 --> 00:35:11,519
[SPEAKER_02] ili tako, ili da prosi.

967
00:35:11,519 --> 00:35:14,639
[SPEAKER_02] Nema nikoga da prosi na ulici tamo.

968
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:16,780
[SPEAKER_02] Sa druge strane,

969
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:18,539
[SPEAKER_02] naravno, postoje velika korupcija,

970
00:35:18,539 --> 00:35:19,780
[SPEAKER_02] veliki nepotizam,

971
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:22,659
[SPEAKER_02] sustavi unutar

972
00:35:22,659 --> 00:35:24,639
[SPEAKER_02] branitelja iz

973
00:35:24,639 --> 00:35:27,079
[SPEAKER_02] iransko-iraškog rata su prešli,

974
00:35:27,079 --> 00:35:28,760
[SPEAKER_02] koji su zapravo postali danas

975
00:35:28,760 --> 00:35:30,500
[SPEAKER_02] ono što je revolucionalna garda

976
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:31,820
[SPEAKER_02] i dobrovoljačke

977
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:32,760
[SPEAKER_02] basiđi

978
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:34,699
[SPEAKER_02] grupacije,

979
00:35:34,699 --> 00:35:36,480
[SPEAKER_02] oni su se obogatili

980
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:38,920
[SPEAKER_02] na paralelnim sustavima

981
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:40,960
[SPEAKER_02] u kojima su preuzimali

982
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,320
[SPEAKER_02] neke državne poduzeće

983
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:42,840
[SPEAKER_02] i tako da.

984
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, samo jedno pitanje

985
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] oko Irana.

986
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjela sam da je

987
00:35:48,159 --> 00:35:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] podignuta crvena zastava

988
00:35:50,559 --> 00:35:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] pred njihovom džamijom,

989
00:35:53,639 --> 00:35:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

990
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] A to se tumači

991
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:57,300
[SPEAKER_00] kao poziv

992
00:35:57,300 --> 00:36:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo na akciju.

993
00:36:00,380 --> 00:36:04,179
[SPEAKER_02] To je malo dublje.

994
00:36:04,179 --> 00:36:07,940
[SPEAKER_02] Naravno, crvena je

995
00:36:07,940 --> 00:36:10,300
[SPEAKER_02] znači iranci su šiti,

996
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:14,219
[SPEAKER_02] crvena boja u šizmu

997
00:36:14,219 --> 00:36:15,599
[SPEAKER_02] predstavlja dvije stvari.

998
00:36:15,599 --> 00:36:18,579
[SPEAKER_02] S jedne strane je mučeništvo.

999
00:36:18,579 --> 00:36:21,780
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, to je znak mučeništva,

1000
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:24,480
[SPEAKER_02] u ostalom i u kršanstvu je

1001
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,820
[SPEAKER_02] crvena boja

1002
00:36:25,820 --> 00:36:26,880
[SPEAKER_02] znak mučenika.

1003
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:29,079
[SPEAKER_02] Kada je, ne znam,

1004
00:36:29,079 --> 00:36:30,219
[SPEAKER_02] kada je Sveti Stjepan

1005
00:36:30,219 --> 00:36:31,500
[SPEAKER_02] nosite crvenu štolu,

1006
00:36:31,500 --> 00:36:34,000
[SPEAKER_02] crvenu misnicu i tako dalje.

1007
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:34,860
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

1008
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:37,920
[SPEAKER_02] to je s jedna strana.

1009
00:36:37,920 --> 00:36:39,699
[SPEAKER_02] s druge strane,

1010
00:36:39,699 --> 00:36:41,440
[SPEAKER_02] crvena je također u nekim

1011
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:43,400
[SPEAKER_02] stvarima znak

1012
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:45,800
[SPEAKER_02] izdajništva,

1013
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,239
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno znak nekoga

1014
00:36:47,239 --> 00:36:48,380
[SPEAKER_02] koji je protivnik.

1015
00:36:48,380 --> 00:36:50,460
[SPEAKER_02] A to je vezano

1016
00:36:50,460 --> 00:36:52,059
[SPEAKER_02] za samu tu

1017
00:36:52,059 --> 00:36:53,780
[SPEAKER_02] glavnu

1018
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:55,860
[SPEAKER_02] ideološku

1019
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,820
[SPEAKER_02] i religijsku priču

1020
00:36:57,820 --> 00:36:58,719
[SPEAKER_02] unuta šizma,

1021
00:36:58,719 --> 00:36:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] to je pogibija

1022
00:36:59,559 --> 00:37:00,840
[SPEAKER_02] imama Huseina,

1023
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:01,320
[SPEAKER_02] unuka

1024
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:03,199
[SPEAKER_02] poslanika Muhameda,

1025
00:37:03,199 --> 00:37:04,480
[SPEAKER_02] koji je ubijen

1026
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:05,820
[SPEAKER_02] od strane muslimana,

1027
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:06,699
[SPEAKER_02] znači od strane

1028
00:37:06,699 --> 00:37:09,500
[SPEAKER_02] islamske jedne dinastije,

1029
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:10,980
[SPEAKER_02] koji su,

1030
00:37:10,980 --> 00:37:12,460
[SPEAKER_02] kad su dolazili

1031
00:37:12,460 --> 00:37:13,159
[SPEAKER_02] u Iraku,

1032
00:37:13,159 --> 00:37:13,880
[SPEAKER_02] na tim poljima

1033
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,400
[SPEAKER_02] Karbale,

1034
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,360
[SPEAKER_02] kad su dolazili

1035
